occMgmtDuplicateCmdDesc: Duplicate the selected assembly based on the defined actions.
occMgmtDuplicateCloneDesc: Mark the object to be saved with a new ID in the duplicated structure. Related children remain as they are in the original structure.
occMgmtDuplicateCloneBelowDesc: Mark the object and its children to be saved with new IDs in the duplicated structure.
occMgmtDuplicateRemoveDesc: Mark the object for removal from the duplicated structure.
occMgmtDuplicateReplaceDesc: Mark for replacement with another object in the duplicated structure.
OccMgmtDuplicateSettingsDesc: Configure how the Duplicate actions will be performed.
OccMgmtDuplicateUndoDesc: Undo the action performed on the selection.
